{
  "id": "kE2SJN9H",
  "slug": "chocolate-quest-repoured",
  "title": "Chocolate Quest Repoured",
  "description": "Spiritual successor of Chocolate Quest / Better Dungeons by Chocolatin. Adds a dungeon system and new mobs and bosses to fight",
  "body": "CQR is a redesign of Chocolate Quest (though you might know it as better dungeons) for Minecraft 1.12.2, and probably eventually the future.\nIf Curseforge is currently broken, you can get the latest build from our website by clicking here.\n\nTHIS MOD REQUIRES GECKOLIB AND REACHFIX IT WILL NOT LAUNCH UNLESS THEY ARE INSTALLED,* YOU CAN GET THEM HERE: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/geckolib, https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/reach-fix \n\n <div class=\"page-content\"><article><span>Chocolate Quest Repoured is the reawakening of the famous BetterDungeons / ChocolateQuest Mod made by Chocolatin!</span><br><br><span>To accomplish this task we had to start from the ground up meaning that this is a completely different mod, however it still is heavily inspired by it.</span><br><span>We hope to give you an awesome experience with this, which is a passion project made possible by a few individuals that spend their free time on this.</span><br><br><span>Below we gave an overview over all the different kinds of dungeons in the main mod you can discover. This however doesn’t cover all of them.</span></article><hr class=\"line-solid\"><div class=\"section-item\"><header>Mighty fortresses</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-6104px); width: 9156px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles/1.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles/2.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles/3.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"3\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"4\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles/5.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"5\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles/6.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"6\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles/7.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"7\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles/8.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"8\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"9\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"10\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-right\"><section>Long ago, the races built large castle like settlements to live there and to defend themselves from the dangers the overworld held for them.</section><br><section>Those strongholds are scattered over the grassy plains and hold quite the reward in them.</section></article></div></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><header>Volcanoes</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description order-reverse\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-1526px); width: 4578px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/volcano/1.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/volcano/2.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/volcano/3.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"3\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/volcano/4.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"4\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-left\"><section>Being gigantic geological structures, full of resources and wealth, they were the best home a dwarf could ever wish for. However, long ago, the dwarven empires were overrun by creatures called Gremlins.</section><br><section>Conquer the volcano, invade the stronghold located inside it and mine all that ore!</section></article></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><header>Plains of frost and snow</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-763px); width: 8393px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles_snow/1.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles_snow/3.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"3\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"4\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"5\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles_snow/6.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"6\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles_snow/7.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"7\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/castles_snow/8.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"8\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"9\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-right\"><section>Banished from their home dimension and despised by all the other races and tribes, the walkers had nowhere to go but the icy, cold, uninhabitable plains they call their territory now.</section><br><section>They live in gigantic fortresses constructed by them eons ago during a long forgotten age.</section></article></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><header>Strongholds</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description order-reverse\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-763px); width: 8393px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/strongholds/3.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"3\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"4\" 