how-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-3815px); width: 6867px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/outposts/1.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/outposts/3.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"3\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"4\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"5\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"6\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"7\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/outposts/1.jpg\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-right\"><section>There are many different races living in the known world. Some of them explore the world like you.</section><br><section>From time to time you can come across a small outpost housing different races from different factions.</section></article></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><header>The depths of the nether</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description order-reverse\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-3052px); width: 5341px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/nether/3.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"3\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"4\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/nether/5.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"5\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-left\"><section>Hidden in the hot depths of the nether’s lava oceans lie the settlements of the boarmen and the minotaurs.</section><br><section>The boarmen build large grid shaped cities that seem to swim in the lava oceans. The minotaurs however managed to find a way to construct large platforms, hanging from massive chains, to build their houses own.</section></article></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><header>Pirates!</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-763px); width: 8393px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/ships/3.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"3\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"4\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"5\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/ships/6.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"6\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"7\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"8\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"9\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-right\"><section>While most races built mighty fortresses or, like the dwarves, dug out great underground bastions, the pirates decided to not do so. Instead they travel the seas and skies to search for potential victims to raid.</section><br><section>There however is the legend of the pirate’s base, being a small island housing their leader and their treasures.</section><br><section>Some even claim to have seen pirates abducting whole ships with one of their mighty airships.</section></article></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><header>Overgrown caves</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description order-reverse\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-1526px); width: 3052px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/caves/1.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/caves/2.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"2\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/caves/1.jpg\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-left\"><section>Deep in the jungles and swamps underneath the surface lie large caves. These caves pose a great habitat for gigantic mushrooms and are a suitable home for gremlins and spiders.</section><br><section>Some even say that in rare cases, these cave’s main chamber breaches through the surface.</section></article></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><header>Mysteries of the known world</header><div class=\"slideshow-with-description\"><div class=\"slideshow-container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" aria-roledescription=\"carousel\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-container\"><div class=\"react-slideshow-wrapper slide \"><div class=\"images-wrap\" style=\"transform: translate(-1526px); width: 2289px;\"><div data-index=\"-1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><span class=\"\" style=\"display: inline-block;\"></span></div></div><div data-index=\"0\" class=\"active\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"false\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/wall/1.jpg\"></div></div><div data-index=\"1\" aria-roledescription=\"slide\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"width: 763px; display: block;\"><div class=\"each-slide\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://dertoaster98.github.io/cq-repoured-website/slides/wall/1.jpg\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-right\"><section>Far in the north of the known world lies a large wall. Adventurers, brave enough to travel there, report it is guarded by ghostly warriors wearing black.</section><br><section>They dedicated their lives to guard that wall. They have forgotten since when they guard. They’ve forgotten for who they guard. And they have forgotten why they guard it. It is the task of the brave adventurers to find out.</section></article></div></div><br><div class=\"section-item\"><hr class=\"line-solid\"><article class=\"slideshow-with-description-left\"><span>Now that you know about the dangers awaiting you, are you brave enough to get your best available gear and fight for your death for the sake of treasure and honor?</span><br><br><span>Small notice: the worldgen in the screenshots is not representative of the end product, you can reproduce them with CQR and biome bundle.</span></article></div></div>",
